snippet.title: Denise, 1973 UFO Encounter, Missing Time?
snippet.description:
A quick interview in Arizona at the MUFON field investigator's boot camp. Denise discusses her near twilight encounter with a friend, a cigar shaped UFO with windows, hieroglyphics and some type of entities. Suddenly was dark outside. Note: Here is a report by another eye witness: https://ufo.net/2017/01/17/rochester-new-york-usa-summer-1973/
I had only five minutes to speak to her, she should be back the first of the year for a longer interview!
 #UAP #1973Sighting #CloseEncounter #cigarUFO
